'''[[guest]] [[book]]'''
#a type of [[ledger]] on which a record of guests to a particular establishment (common examples being [[bed and breakfast]]s and [[museum]]s) is voluntarily updated by the guests themselves upon leaving. It would generally consist of the guest's name, the date, and any (polite) comments the guest had about the place.
#a feature of a web site perfoming a similar function to a physical guest book